{"tid":311491,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先一開機，電腦大爆炸","createTime":"2017-07-06T15:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T13:38:46.000Z","uid":28918,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9502c184aedbf993d02648bddc13c3fa500fdf9","tid":311491,"uid":28918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"部機用左兩年半，用得都好正常<br />\n<br />\n今晚照舊開機，開左一陣都未login, 部機已經出煙同有燶味，<br />\n<br />\n我拆制頭諗住拎起顯示卡再開，<br />\n<br />\n點知一開制就噗一聲大響，老母板發出應該，仲有火花，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n爆完之後全屋跳制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問點解會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋harddisk會唔會冇哂資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fd5bb818eec456da2cedf66e0f8e2a2372a60d","tid":311491,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"拎左宇宙通行證未"},{"pid":"9ce89c0b9409b26974ecc30bd9d2f610846e6b63","tid":311491,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"有冇相睇"},{"pid":"02c81eea1824e4c87d865381898b5028bb7e6223","tid":311491,"uid":14487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"跑車牛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cee97d06e13b8bbbd60d200ce17afc6c8e63284","tid":311491,"uid":28918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockqu